{!</table>!}

- @start: Let us start the conclave...

@start
audio: music/VeniCreatorSpiritus-CantoGregoriano.mp3
face-image: img/DoorClose.jpg

There are three factions of the Holy See, the reformist, the centrist or commonly referred as pragmatists and traditionalist.

Cardinal Parolin, a reformist candidate has asked the assembled cardinal if they wish to postpone the vote until morning.

- @continue: Continue the vote.
- @postpone: Postpone the vote.

@postpone
choose-if: resources == 0
unavailable-subtitle: No, we will not pursue this.

Postpone wow

@continue

